assetName: localhost:8000 - No Support for POST/OPTIONS/DELETE Methods
description: SimpleHTTPServer only supports GET and HEAD methods. POST, OPTIONS, DELETE, PUT, PATCH and other HTTP methods return 501 Unsupported method errors.
notes: This is a limitation of SimpleHTTPServer intended for static file serving only. Prevents any form submission or API functionality. Indicates this is a development/demo environment, not a production system. No backend functionality available."
